| Business Concern | BC‑Driven Solution | Quantifiable Benefit |
|-------------------|-------------------|----------------------|
| **Revenue loss from outages** | Automated fail‑over & rapid alerts | $360 k saved per 8‑h outage (30 % reduction) |
| **Regulatory fines** | Centralised audit‑trail | $30 k‑$200 k penalty avoidance annually |
| **Higher insurance premiums** | Documented continuity evidence | 10‑15 % premium discount (≈ $12 k / yr) |
